The paper discusses the basic principle of diffusion-based molecular communication, which involves information coding and modulation techniques, system performance analysis, and multi-hop nano-networks. These topics are related to information theory (cs.IT), neural networks (cs.NE), network infrastructure (cs.NI), control systems (cs.SY), and bioinformatics (cs.BIO).
